														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2525101">
									

<p>Part 1 of 2. Theme song is <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-KjnlmdA3T4">J-35 Draken</a>, by <a href="https://dubmood.bandcamp.com/">Dubmood</a>.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Shoutout&nbsp;to&nbsp;all&nbsp;these&nbsp;folks&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;Hide&nbsp;thanks</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Huge huge huge thanks to GreenWolf, TwistedGears, and TyGently for looking at this mechanical monster nearly every step of the way, convincing me to rewrite this entirely from scratch and rethink pretty much everything about it, and then pointing out what was bad about the rewrite.<br />
Huge huge thanks to SunnyClockwork and Randomini for pointing out issues with the plot's cohesiveness and helping me figure out how to fix those issues.<br />
Huge thanks to Moenennbys, MrWrong, Metaphysician, Timetraveling, Cimmerian, BeardedPotato, ParaDLell, psul, Jacob Conwell, kola, AidenEldritch, Decibelle, minmin, ColonelCairn, LtShwa, Ap0plexic, and anqxyr for their feedback.<br />
And thanks to everyone else I pestered for the last two months for looking at this!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>If anyone could help me figure out why the Google Fonts CSS clashes with the wiki css theme to turn all the robot text into Times New Roman that would be hugely appreciated.</p>
<p>See more of my work on my <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-arvind-desais-personnel-file">author page</a>!</p>

